+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 OR BSD-2-Clause
+/*
+ * LRNG auxiliary interfaces
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2022 Stephan Mueller <smueller@chronox.de>
+ * Copyright (C) 2017 Jason A. Donenfeld <Jason@zx2c4.com>. All
+ * Rights Reserved.
